rows.label: tev041801_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Rada about tyrants in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0001
rows.name:
Oblivia has many terrifying beasts.
Every day brought new scare.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0002
rows.name:
Beware of Edgardo, the Carefree.
He hides behind columns of North Coast.
Jumps out when you least expect it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0003
rows.name:
It was hard to feel free with such monster about.
I was always looking over shoulder.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0004
rows.name:
Do not tell my brother of this! He will laugh at me.
Call me craven.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0005
rows.name:
In exchange for keeping secret, I will tell one.
There are many delicious cosse beans by Lake Basel.
You can have them all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0008
rows.name:
I used to be frightened of hunt.
My legs trembled as soon as beast appeared.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0009
rows.name: But facing death let me find courage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0010
rows.name: Even my brother thinks me better now! Ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0011
rows.name:
But I will be stronger still. I will be legendary warrior.
Carry home heads of many Cavern Clan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0016
rows.name:
I dislike fighting on and off battlefield.
I need patient mate who does not argue.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0017
rows.name:
Last thing I want is crazy female like Vendura,
the Spellbinder. Do you know her, Earth alien?
Cavern Clan warrior from Mesa Fortress?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041801_MSG0018
rows.name:
Marrying her would lead to horrible life of servitude.
I will keep looking for nice mate instead![ST:wait ]
